Pumpkin Soup
Ingredients
1.2 kg / 2.4 lb pumpkin (any type) OR butternut squash, unpeeled weight (Note 1)
1 onion , sliced (white, brown, yellow)
2 garlic cloves , peeled whole
3 cups vegetable or chicken broth/stock , low sodium
1 cup water
Salt and pepper
1/2 â€“ 3/4 cup cream

Place the pumpkin, onion, garlic, broth and water in a pot.Bring to a boil, uncovered, then reduce heat and let simmer rapidly until pumpkin is tender
Remove from heat and blend until smooth. Optional: serve with cream 


